                    <li>Anthropic. (2025). Claude Code overview. <a href="https://docs.anthropic.com/en/docs/claude-code/overview" rel="noopener">docs.anthropic.com/en/docs/claude-code/overview</a></li>
                    <li>Anthropic. (2025). Agent Skills. <a href="https://docs.anthropic.com/en/docs/agents-and-tools/agent-skills" rel="noopener">docs.anthropic.com/en/docs/agents-and-tools/agent-skills</a></li>
